  "title": "Strumming Patterns for Beginners",
  "lessonText": "Learn essential strumming patterns to enhance your guitar playing.",
  "data": {
    "content": "- Start with a simple downstroke pattern.\n- Practice alternating between downstrokes and upstrokes.\n- Use a metronome to keep time.\n- Experiment with different rhythms.\n- Focus on keeping a steady tempo.\n- Gradually increase the complexity of your patterns."
  }
}
